fication is fleeting true fulfillment takes time but offers greater potential reward time is a terrible thing to waste investors misperceptions about what impacts their outcomes often make them spend too much time measuring what doesnt matter and not enough time on what does its time to start looking at what really counts when choosing an investment manager more time for active how does investor tolerance for underperformance line up with their understanding of a longterm perspective our active sentiment study looked at their thoughts behaviors and the connections between the two growing recognizing potential takes insight making something of it takes passion and patience making sense of misalignment given the powerful relationship between decisionmaking and time a misalignment between the two can significantly impact investment outcomes its time to break through that disconnect – and better align asset management delegation decisions with investor time horizons riding the s curve of creative disruption the scurve which shows the growth trajectory of a company creating a new product or even a new industry can be an ally or enemy for investors skilled active managers try to find these companies much earlier on in the curve with an eye toward tapping greater growth potential crafting when patience action and insight work in harmony risk can be an ally not an adversary risk management it’s all about culture for many investors risk is frequently an unwelcome four letter word we are all too familiar with the painful consequences of unforeseen and excessive risks taken in the financial markets not least of all the economic fallout from the global financial crisis in – and yet in the investment context it is a truism that returns can only be generated when calculated risks are taken risk managing from all angles in the countless discussions ive had with clients about the best way to manage risk in a portfolio the critical takeaway is always the same effective risk management isnt any one practice but rather an entire process — an integral part of the firms investment management process to be more specific × mfs investment management canada limited  pmac mfs investment management canada limited  pmac skip to content for investors view firm profile back to search mfs investment management canada limited address  king street west th floor toronto ontario mk b     wwwmfscom principal contacts christine girvan managing director of sales tel     cgirvanmfscom client minimums no private client minimum has been specified institutional  types of accounts managed institutional investor  pension plan institutional investor  nonprofit institutional investor  first nations institutional investor  other provinces of business alberta british columbia manitoba new brunswick newfoundland and labrador nova scotia ontario prince edward island quebec saskatchewan northwest territories nunavut yukon united states  indicates a physical location in this province since opening our doors in  mfs investment management canada limited has grown to become one of canada’s most respected investment management companies from offices in toronto montréal vancouver and chicago we manage over  billion on behalf of pension foundation  endowment private wealth and mutual fund clients we take a team approach to investing which allows our clients to take advantage of the collective strength of our various investment managers and analysts we create separate teams that are comprised of three to seven individuals who build model portfolios for asset mix canadian equities growth value and core global equities growth value and core us equities eafe europe australasia and far east equities and fixed income however no team is ever complete without you the client as the decisions of each of our teams are implemented according to your investment objectives this is why our portfolio managers stress the importance of regular meetings with you so that we are constantly aware of all of your requirements and wishes mfs investment management canada limited’s success is based in large part on an entrepreneurial team culture as ownermanagers we focus on running the business with a long term view and are strongly incented to maintain superior investment research establish longrun succession planning facilitate steady growth and uphold the highest service standards on a longterm basis management owns  of the firm with share ownership currently spread among  partners and sun life financial corp owning the balance the mfs investment management canada limited team consists of over  employees including  portfolio managers of whom  are research analysts to learn more about mfs investment management canada limited and how we would work together please get in touch we look forward to it five areas distinguish mfs investment management canada limited proven investment management philosophy our firm uses a teambased majority voting approach to investment management decisions are made by experienced teams of investment managers supported by a globally oriented group of research analysts this process integrates decisionmaking and research to maximize synergies regarding idea generation and portfolio structure depth of our research expertise the recognized research expertise within each of our investment management groups enables us to emphasize internal proprietary research in our investment process research is done on a global basis equity management process by using integrated equity management teams and structuring their responsibilities along global sectors we have allowed every equity strategy to be managed on a truly global basis all portfolios have focused approaches that have clearly defined risk controls strong stable organization and ability to effectively handle management transition we have an experienced management group which is diversified by age we are committed to having a management structure which provides orderly personnel succession and is not overly dependent on any particular individual the investment groups operate in a disciplined democratic fashion while maintaining our longterm investment philosophy we have been managing money successfully since  and have demonstrated our ability to handle management changes superior service our client retention rate is high and in part this has been the result of the strong rapport we have built with plan sponsors and investment committees our investment reviews are structured to make our investment results and intentions clear and concise we regularly consult with clients to ensure they are provided with the information they require   mfs mclean budden becomes mfs investment management canada limited  business wire mfs mclean budden becomes mfs investment management canada limited name change demonstrates local commitment aligns with global brand november    am eastern standard time boston  torontobusiness wireglobal asset manager mfs® has announced a name change to its canadian operations mfs mclean budden is now mfs investment management canada limited the name change reflects the consistency of the mfs brand and aligns the canadian division with mfs global operations the canadian market represents a key area of focus for mfs said michael roberge mfs president and chief investment officer “a local presence is important to mfs our regional canadian investment teams help deliver realtime knowledge and insights to their mfs counterparts around the world that same approach employed globally by mfs in other local markets enhances the knowledge and insights available to our canadian investment teams they work collaboratively across sectors and asset classes as part of plus person investment team to the benefit of our clients globally” in september  mfs parent company sun life financial merged mclean budden with mfs significantly increasing mfs presence in canada today mfs’ global research platform benefits from a team of  canadian investment professionals based in toronto offering local investment insight including trading working collaboratively across eight global sector teams client relations sales marketing legal and other operational functions are conducted in toronto montreal and vancouver as well the new name extends the consistency of our brand identity and our global approach said carol geremia president of mfs institutional advisors inc in addition it represents the importance mfs places on its canadian business and our inherent promise to deliver a world class client experience that clients around the world have come to expect” the name change took effect november   for more information visit the new institutions  consultants web site for canadian investors on mfscom about mfs investment management mfs is an active global asset manager with investment offices in boston hong kong london mexico city são paulo singapore sydney tokyo and toronto we employ a uniquely collaborative approach to build better insights for our clients our investment approach has three core elements of integrated research global collaboration and active risk management established in  mfs manages us billion in assets on behalf of individual and institutional investors worldwide as of september   please visit mfscom for more information mfs investment management huntington avenue boston ma   contacts mfs investment managementjames aber ordan flaherty  release summary mfs mclean budden is now mfs investment management canada limited contacts mfs investment managementjames aber ordan flaherty  search advanced news search advanced news search log in sign up microsoft personalized ad preferences to opt out of personalized ads in this browser your browser history must allow firstparty and thirdparty cookies and you must have your browsing experience set to not delete browsing history on exit instructions for enabling cookies and configuring your browsing history may be available in your browsers settings privacy or help documentation sign in hold on